"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/882675","Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government","false","2018-04-18","<p>As part of exploratory analysis into the determinants of house prices, the Department published the relevant analysis on 13 April and it is available here:</p><p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/analysis-of-the-determinants-of-house-price-changes" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/analysis-of-the-determinants-of-house-price-changes</a>.</p><p>I will place a copy in the Library of both houses.</p>","Esher and Walton","Dominic Raab","135738","2018-04-18T10:15:53.27Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/882675/answer","Biography information for Dominic Raab","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/882675/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/882675/answer",,,,,"7","Housing, Communities and Local Government","Housing, Communities and Local Government","2018-04-13","Housing: Prices","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Housing, Communities and Local Government, if he will place a copy of any unpublished evidence held by his Department on the effect of immigration on house prices in the Library of the House of Commons.","false","Biography information for John Healey","Wentworth and Dearne","John Healey","135737"
